{"tid":724794,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃秋生前外遇嫁外籍男 一家五口曝光","createTime":"2018-07-01T08:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T08:19:25.000Z","uid":160973,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5068d92fb5f0ce5a0b8cac64bad64e7cc432bcf6","tid":724794,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:01:30.000Z","msg":"黃秋生前外遇Joyce已嫁外籍男, 而且已育有一子一女。黃秋生的私生子William 生母Joyce突然爆料，有報道指Joyce是岑建勳的外甥女，秋生因直接入生活費俾阿仔，因而令她爆料，身在英國的阿仔目前住在酒店。秋生回覆本刊說：「其實發生今次件事就係因為佢叫阿仔返嚟香港搞身份證，我決定以後將啲錢直接俾阿仔而起，佢覺得我要將俾阿仔的錢分一半俾佢。阿仔返到去英國後話我知，阿媽話佢幫住我，唔俾佢入屋，趕咗佢走，咁我叫佢住幾日酒店先，他之後去咗朋友度住，阿仔啱啱同我講，話阿媽爆完大鑊後，自己心情好好，叫佢返屋企，我叫阿仔唔好啦！返去執嘢，因為唔知佢幾時心情唔好又趕佢走，反正兩個月後入大學宿舍，我叫佢在外面租屋住兩個月先，我最唔想影響阿仔讀書的心情。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2MxyJS4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MxyJS4&d=jR4AI4tUEnMBLdsrLzKp4sn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=79813662\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2MxyJS4</a>"},{"pid":"9cdddba0afcbda8c2ffd066e884b39d510751190","tid":724794,"uid":5253,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:04:31.000Z","msg":"生前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d846851aed89b4982bb24d5e4f0a52a731c924c0","tid":724794,"uid":75137,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:06:46.000Z","msg":"正臭雞  淨係識得問人拎錢"},{"pid":"de1011b3696cefbfc81380b7c2dd1fa9793ed25f","tid":724794,"uid":39256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cdddba0afcbda8c2ffd066e884b39d510751190","tid":724794,"uid":5253,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:04:31.000Z","msg":"生前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:07:26.000Z","msg":"睇一眼我都係望到生前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2e72f9bc2bb5224aa25b87ef69ee6e5defd72b","tid":724794,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:10:43.000Z","msg":"搵外遇都唔搵件正啲，人生有幾多次外遇"},{"pid":"739f2bfaba7fdc172e099db64590bf7e02ab07cc","tid":724794,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:19:06.000Z","msg":"黃秋係乜水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388faa00d52a8ff8798d71ef6a0e9fc787b78265","tid":724794,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"死臭閪嫁撚左仲要問人攞錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}